'''''Abi foq al-Shagara''''' (Data Hejuru ku Giti), ni filime yo mu Misiri yo mu 1969 ikinamico yerekana urukundo yakozwe na Hussein Kamal ikorwa na Abdel Halim Hafez kuri Sawt al-Fann.   Muri iyi filime hagaragaramo Abdel Halim Hafez na Nadia Lutfi mu mwanya wa mbere aho nka Mervat Amin Jenita Furneau, Samir Sabri na Salah Nazmi bagize uruhare runini. 

Filime yafatiwe muri Alegizandiriya no mu micungararo yayo.  Filime yabaye amashusho yuwo mwaka cyane  kubera gusomana. Filime ifatwa nkimwe muri firime nziza zigeze gukorwa mu Misiri.  Nibigaragara bwa firime ya nyuma yakozwe n'umukinnyi wa filime Abdel Halim Hafez mbere y'urupfu rwe ku ya 30 Werurwe 1977 kubera kunanirwa kw'umwijima nk'ikibazo cya ''Schistosoma mansoni'' . 

